'''2013年环意自行车赛'''是第96届[[环意自行车赛|环意自行车赛]]，于2013年5月4日至26日进行，此次比赛是2013年UCI世界巡回赛的其中一站比赛<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.telegraph.co.uk/sport/othersports/cycling/10036711/Giro-dItalia-2013-stage-by-stage-guide-to-the-96th-edition-of-la-corsa-rosa.html|title=Giro d'Italia 2013: stage-by-stage guide to the 96th edition of la corsa rosa|publisher=The Telegraph|date=2013-05-04|accessdate=2020-09-29|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130506104010/https://www.telegraph.co.uk/sport/othersports/cycling/10036711/Giro-dItalia-2013-stage-by-stage-guide-to-the-96th-edition-of-la-corsa-rosa.html|archivedate=2013-05-06|dead-url=no}}</ref>。比赛共分为21个赛段，起点位于[[那不勒斯|那不勒斯]]，终点位于[[布雷西亚|布雷西亚]]<ref name=route>{{cite news|last=Brown|first=Gregor|title=Giro d'Italia 2013 route presented|url=http://www.cyclingweekly.co.uk/news/latest/534977/giro-d-italia-2013-route-presented.html|work=Cycling Weekly|accessdate=2013-05-10|date=2012-09-30|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121004030925/http://www.cyclingweekly.co.uk/news/latest/534977/giro-d-italia-2013-route-presented.html|archivedate=2012-10-04|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

共有23支车队参加此次比赛，其中19支为世界职业车队，另外4支为洲际职业车队。赛事主办方原定和往届一样安排18支世界职业车队和4支洲际职业车队参赛<ref>{{cite news|last=Farrand|first=Stephen|title=Bardiani, Colombia and Fantini Vini secure Giro d'Italia wild card invitations|url=http://www.cyclingnews.com/news/bardiani-colombia-and-fantini-vini-secure-giro-ditalia-wild-card-invitations|work=Cyclingnews.com|accessdate=2013-02-19|date=2013-01-08|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130111080741/http://www.cyclingnews.com/news/bardiani-colombia-and-fantini-vini-secure-giro-ditalia-wild-card-invitations|archivedate=2013-01-11|dead-url=no}}</ref>。然而由于先前被排除出世界职业车队行列的[[Katusha车队|Katusha车队]]通过向[[国际体育仲裁法庭|国际体育仲裁法庭]]提出上诉，成功夺回世界职业车队的地位，而[[国际自行车联合会|国际自行车联合会]]亦不希望取消其他车队的参赛资格，至此此次比赛的参赛车队数较往届增加一支。<ref>{{cite news|title=UCI confirms 19 WorldTour teams for 2013|url=http://www.cyclingnews.com/news/uci-confirms-19-worldtour-teams-for-2013|work=Cyclingnews.com|accessdate=2013-02-19|date=2013-02-18|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130221004754/http://www.cyclingnews.com/news/uci-confirms-19-worldtour-teams-for-2013|archivedate=2013-02-21|dead-url=no}}</ref>

最终来自阿斯塔纳车队的[[溫琴佐·尼巴利|溫琴佐·尼巴利]]获得此次比赛的总冠军。来自天空车队的[[Rigoberto_Urán|Rigoberto Urán]]获得第二名，这一成绩是1995年以来哥伦比亚选手在环意自行车赛的最好名次。来自BMC Racing Team的澳大利亚选手[[卡德尔·埃文斯|卡德尔·埃文斯]]则获得第三名。<ref name=ESPN_recap>{{cite news|title=What we learned from the 2013 Giro|author=Andrew Hood|date=2013-05-28|publisher=ESPN|url=http://espn.go.com/sports/endurance/story/_/id/9318868/endurance-sports-learned-2013-giro-ditalia|accessdate=2013-05-29|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160305042400/http://espn.go.com/sports/endurance/story/_/id/9318868/endurance-sports-learned-2013-giro-ditalia|archivedate=2016-03-05|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=Bicycling_recap>{{cite news|title=2013 Giro d'Italia: Winners and Losers|author=Whit Yost|work=Bicycling|url=http://www.bicycling.com/news/pro-cycling/2013-giro-d-italia-winners-and-losers|accessdate=2013-05-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130613033026/http://www.bicycling.com/news/pro-cycling/2013-giro-d-italia-winners-and-losers|archive-date=2013-06-13|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

